\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Why-Should-Businesses-Consider-Marketo-Consulting-Services-Today.mp3\">\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"swp_song_details player_entry_left\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"play_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-play before_song compact_bs\"><\/i>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"player_song_name transition3\" data-albumname=\"Pear Tree Restaurant\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tSwinging Christmas\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"entry_duration mpfe_fix_lh\"><\/span>\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"song_buy_icons compact_buy_icons transition3 clearfix mobile_visibility_hide\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2003a45 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2003a45\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-1\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8820442 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8820442\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Everyone is trying to hit the bullseye with flawless campaign strategy however a right choice of tools in your arsenal is important. A crucial part of this strategy is marketing automation. While email automation is often considered a component of<a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/marketing-automation\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> marketing automation<\/a>, it\u2019s important to note that it\u2019s not an alternative. Marketing automation tools offer far more power in multiple areas of Revenue Operations and flexibility than basic email tools.<\/p><p>For example, SendGrid is a great tool for email deliverability, especially for transactional emails, but it lacks the advanced automation features needed for comprehensive marketing strategies. This is where platforms like Pardot and Salesforce Marketing Cloud (SFMC) come into play. Both are owned by Salesforce and are top contenders in the marketing automation space. Let\u2019s dive into a comparison of Pardot and <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/salesforce-marketing-cloud\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Salesforce Marketing Cloud<\/a> to help you determine which is best for your business.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-72113a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"72113a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Basics:<\/strong> Before we get into the detailed pros and cons, it\u2019s important to understand the basics of these platforms:<\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Pardot:<\/strong> Pardot is a marketing automation tool designed to help businesses with lead generation, qualification, nurturing, and aligning sales efforts. It\u2019s particularly well-suited for companies with longer sales cycles and complex B2B relationships. It can also fit a high ticket B2C model as well.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Salesforce Marketing Cloud (SFMC):<\/strong> SFMC is a comprehensive marketing automation platform that handles both B2B and B2C marketing. Originally known as ExactTarget, SFMC is designed for large-scale, complex marketing operations, offering extensive capabilities for customer engagement and journey automation.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c0f628 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0c0f628\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pros of Pardot:<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7898f76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7898f76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>User-Friendly Interface:<\/strong> Pardot offers a seamless and intuitive experience, especially if you\u2019re familiar with Salesforce. Navigating, creating emails, and managing campaigns are straightforward tasks.<\/p><p><strong>Seamless Salesforce Integration:<\/strong> As a part of the Salesforce ecosystem, Pardot integrates perfectly with Salesforce CRM, ensuring smooth data flow and unified reporting.<\/p><p><strong>Lead Scoring and Nurturing:<\/strong> Pardot excels at lead management, providing advanced lead scoring and nurturing capabilities that help sales teams focus on the most promising leads.<\/p><p><strong>ROI Tracking:<\/strong> Pardot offers strong reporting tools that allow businesses to accurately track and measure the ROI of their marketing efforts.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-079a7e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"079a7e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Pros-and-Cons-of-Pardot-vs-Salesforce-qtmo77x811m7wd4j2h816cskuy3irfpr4hd2r5cyeo.jpg\" title=\"Pros and Cons of Pardot vs Salesforce\" alt=\"Pros and Cons of Pardot vs Salesforce\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b13cca all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6b13cca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Cons of Pardot:<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-987f4a8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"987f4a8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Limited B2C Capabilities:<\/strong> While Pardot is powerful for B2B, it may not offer the level of sophistication required for B2C marketing, particularly when it comes to managing large consumer databases.<\/p><p><strong>Basic Email Design:<\/strong> Pardot\u2019s email builder is functional but may feel limited if you need highly customized or visually dynamic emails.<\/p><p><strong>High Cost for B2C:<\/strong> Pardot can be expensive for B2C campaigns, especially if you\u2019re dealing with a large number of leads.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cb784de all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cb784de\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pros of Salesforce Marketing Cloud:<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4176004 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4176004\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Comprehensive Integration:<\/strong> SFMC offers seamless integration with <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/salesforce\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Salesforce CRM<\/a> through Marketing Cloud Connect, enabling real-time data synchronization and unified campaign management.<\/p><p><strong>Advanced Data Management:<\/strong> SFMC shines with its ability to handle multiple data points from various sources, allowing for complex segmentation and targeting.<\/p><p><strong>Automation Studio:<\/strong> SFMC provides powerful automation tools, including Automation Studio and Journey Builder, enabling you to create sophisticated, multi-step marketing campaigns.<\/p><p><strong>Scalability:<\/strong> SFMC is built to handle large-scale marketing operations, making it ideal for enterprises with extensive customer bases and complex needs.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dd939d0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"dd939d0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Pros-of-Salesforce-Marketing-Cloud-qwadds55oqmojvmi2543r6n6r8ymq5kg6yt85rxv00.jpg\" title=\"Pros of Salesforce Marketing Cloud\" alt=\"Pros of Salesforce Marketing Cloud\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d7325e elementor-widget-tablet__width-initial all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8d7325e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Cons of Salesforce Marketing Cloud:<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c55492 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5c55492\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Complexity:<\/strong> SFMC is a robust platform, but its extensive capabilities come with a steep learning curve. Proper training is often required to fully utilize its features.<\/p><p><strong>High Cost:<\/strong> SFMC is a premium product with a price tag to match. Additional features like Mobile Studio and Advertising Studio come at an extra cost, further increasing the overall investment.<\/p><p><strong>Limited Basic Reporting:<\/strong> Similar to Pardot, SFMC\u2019s basic reporting can be limited. To unlock its full potential, you\u2019ll need to invest in the Marketing Intelligence Suite, which adds to the complexity and cost.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e74727b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e74727b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Discover how integrating AI and IoT with Salesforce can unlock powerful marketing automation possibilities in <a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/blog\/salesforce-integrations-ai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Salesforce Integrations: Bridging AI, IoT, and Legacy Systems Seamlessly<\/a>.<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-835e62e all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"835e62e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conclusion<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33365ef elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"33365ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Choosing between Pardot and Salesforce Marketing Cloud depends on your business needs. If you\u2019re focused on B2B marketing, lead generation, and nurturing, Pardot is a great choice. However, if your needs are more complex and you require extensive data management and customer journey automation, Salesforce Marketing Cloud might be the better option.<\/p><p>In summary, use Salesforce Marketing Cloud if you have complex marketing needs and a larger budget, and consider Pardot for more targeted B2B campaigns or high-value B2C efforts. We\u2019d love to hear your thoughts\u2014let us know which platform you prefer and why. Thank you!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-d6b991c\" data-id=\"d6b991c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-224d9df elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"224d9df\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;],&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-a7f692a\" data-id=\"a7f692a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9200702 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9200702\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Latest WhitePaper<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7ae9ba9 elementor-grid-1 elementor-grid-tablet-2 elementor-grid-mobile-1 elementor-posts--thumbnail-top elementor-posts__hover-gradient elementor-widget elementor-widget-